---
import Layout from '../../Base.astro';
import SimpleHero from '../../components/SimpleHero.astro';
import FeaturedArticles from '../../components/FeaturedArticles.astro';
import ServicesRelatedWork from '../../components/ServicesRelatedWork.astro';
import '../../styles/pages/_services-list.scss';
---

<Layout
  title="Motion Graphics | Florida Video Production Services"
  description="When the story is complex, static visuals can only carry so much weight. We use motion graphics to explain, emphasize, and make important ideas easier to remember."
>
  <SimpleHero
    tagline="Content Creation Services"
    title="Motion Graphics"
    description="When the story is complex, static visuals can only carry so much weight. We use motion graphics to explain, emphasize, and make important ideas easier to remember."
    lottieFile="motion-graphics.json"
  />
  <div class="service-body">
    <div class="wrapper wrapper--narrow">
      <h2>Where teams get stuck</h2>
      <p>
        Some ideas are hard to explain with static visuals alone. Products, processes, data, and layered stories often
        need more pacing and more guidance than a still graphic can provide.
      </p>
      <p>When attention is limited, motion can help the audience follow the idea instead of dropping off halfway through it.</p>
      <h2>How we fix it</h2>
      <p>We use animation, pacing, typography, sound, and sequencing to make the message easier to understand and more memorable once it lands.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Case studies</li>
        <li>Data visualizations</li>
        <li>Product reviews</li>
        <li>Explainer videos</li>
        <li>Testimonials</li>
        <li>Promotion</li>
        <li>Sales collateral</li>
        <li>Social media</li>
      </ul>
      <h2>What moving forward looks like</h2>
      <p>If you need to explain a process, launch something new, or turn data into a more watchable story, we can map the concept, recommend the right format, and build a motion piece around the outcome you need.</p>
      <p><a href="/contact/" class="button button--green">Talk Through Your Motion Project</a></p>
    </div>
    <ServicesRelatedWork tag={76} />
  </div>
  <FeaturedArticles />
</Layout>
